{"_id": "0665443cbdefa72b", "name": "Protective Pads", "type": "item", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "<p>With this pads on you won't come into direct contact with the foe during close-range combat. Moves and Abilities that activate due to a Non-Ranged Physical Move do not trigger for the user.</p>", "price": null, "rarity": "Not for Sale", "pocket": "heldItem"}, "effects": [], "source": "Core 3.0", "flags": {}, "_stats": {"systemId": "pokerole", "systemVersion": "v3.0", "coreVersion": "3.348", "createdTime": 1670695293664, "modifiedTime": 1784006564.849911, "lastModifiedBy": "Generator"}}
{"_id": "f1698f273a2197d0", "name": "Protein", "type": "item", "img": "systems/pokerole/images/items/protein.png", "system": {"description": "<p>A tasty milkshake that aids in the growth of bigger and stronger muscles.</p>", "price": 9800, "rarity": "", "pocket": "medicine"}, "effects": [], "source": "Core 3.0", "flags": {}, "_stats": {"systemId": "pokerole", "systemVersion": "v3.0", "coreVersion": "3.348", "createdTime": 1670695293664, "modifiedTime": 1784006564.858479, "lastModifiedBy": "Generator"}}
{"_id": "0d2be7b1105a135d", "name": "Psychium Z", "type": "item", "img": "systems/pokerole/images/items/psychium-z.png", "system": {"description": "<p>It converts Z-Power into crystals that upgrade Psychic-type moves to Psychic-type Z-Moves.</p>", "price": null, "rarity": "Not for Sale", "pocket": "heldItem"}, "effects": [], "source": "Core 3.0+", "flags": {}, "_stats": {"systemId": "pokerole", "systemVersion": "v3.0", "coreVersion": "3.348", "createdTime": 1670695293664, "modifiedTime": 1784006564.866566, "lastModifiedBy": "Generator"}}
{"_id": "8eae8c7c07968c49", "name": "Quick Ball", "type": "item", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "<p>Uncommon. The seal on this ball works on a timer. Starting with a max potency of 9 dice on the first Round of battle and reducing the seal potency by 2 each Round that passes.</p>", "price": null, "rarity": "Not for Sale", "pocket": "pokeball"}, "effects": [], "source": "Core 3.0", "flags": {}, "_stats": {"systemId": "pokerole", "systemVersion": "v3.0", "coreVersion": "3.348", "createdTime": 1670695293664, "modifiedTime": 1784006564.875042, "lastModifiedBy": "Generator"}}
{"_id": "f5fdcc56f56e4051", "name": "Quick Claw", "type": "item", "img": "systems/pokerole/images/items/quick-claw.png", "system": {"description": "<p>These light and sharp claws make you excited to test them out in combat. Increase user's Initiative roll by 2.</p>", "price": null, "rarity": "Not for Sale", "pocket": "heldItem"}, "effects": [], "source": "Core 3.0", "flags": {}, "_stats": {"systemId": "pokerole", "systemVersion": "v3.0", "coreVersion": "3.348", "createdTime": 1670695293664, "modifiedTime": 1784006564.882855, "lastModifiedBy": "Generator"}}
{"_id": "75d608b913946729", "name": "Rare Candy", "type": "item", "img": "systems/pokerole/images/items/rare-candy.png", "system": {"description": "<p>You should never accept candy from strangers. ...but maybe just this once.</p>", "price": null, "rarity": "Not for Sale", "pocket": "medicine"}, "effects": [], "source": "Core 3.0", "flags": {}, "_stats": {"systemId": "pokerole", "systemVersion": "v3.0", "coreVersion": "3.348", "createdTime": 1670695293664, "modifiedTime": 1784006564.891433, "lastModifiedBy": "Generator"}}
{"_id": "3f494403201d185f", "name": "Rawst Berry", "type": "item", "img": "systems/pokerole/images/items/rawst-berry.png", "system": {"description": "<p>Its liquid pulp is ideal to stop fire from spreading and numbs the pain on the area. It is quite bitter, though. Heal 1st & 2nd Degree Burn.</p>", "price": null, "rarity": "Uncommon", "pocket": "medicine"}, "effects": [], "source": "Core 3.0", "flags": {}, "_stats": {"systemId": "pokerole", "systemVersion": "v3.0", "coreVersion": "3.348", "createdTime": 1670695293664, "modifiedTime": 1784006564.89926, "lastModifiedBy": "Generator"}}
{"_id": "ef72037e83a03f84", "name": "Razor Claw", "type": "item", "img": "systems/pokerole/images/items/razor-claw.png", "system": {"description": "<p>Deadly claws that trigger Evolution on certain Pokémon. All Physical and Special Moves get the High Critical Effect.</p>", "price": null, "rarity": "Not for Sale", "pocket": "heldItem"}, "effects": [], "source": "Core 3.0", "flags": {}, "_stats": {"systemId": "pokerole", "systemVersion": "v3.0", "coreVersion": "3.348", "createdTime": 1670695293664, "modifiedTime": 1784006564.907754, "lastModifiedBy": "Generator"}}
{"_id": "0fe4cd8e345e2a6d", "name": "Razor Fang", "type": "item", "img": "systems/pokerole/images/items/razor-fang.png", "system": {"description": "<p>Sharp fangs that trigger Evolution on certain Pokémon. Add 1 Chance dice to Flinch on all Physical Moves.</p>", "price": null, "rarity": "Not for Sale", "pocket": "heldItem"}, "effects": [], "source": "Core 3.0", "flags": {}, "_stats": {"systemId": "pokerole", "systemVersion": "v3.0", "coreVersion": "3.348", "createdTime": 1670695293664, "modifiedTime": 1784006564.915625, "lastModifiedBy": "Generator"}}
{"_id": "cba2073047aff9ad", "name": "Red Card", "type": "item", "img": "systems/pokerole/images/items/red-card.png", "system": {"description": "<p>Send an offending Pokémon to the bench! After receiving damage, activate the Switcher effect for the foe. Effect activates only once per Round.</p>", "price": null, "rarity": "Not for Sale", "pocket": "heldItem"}, "effects": [], "source": "Core 3.0", "flags": {}, "_stats": {"systemId": "pokerole", "systemVersion": "v3.0", "coreVersion": "3.348", "createdTime": 1670695293664, "modifiedTime": 1784006564.924577, "lastModifiedBy": "Generator"}}
{"_id": "136fc1753b81cbaf", "name": "Regional Map", "type": "item", "img": "systems/pokerole/images/items/regional-map.png", "system": {"description": "<p>A map with the marked routes, cities and Pokémon Centers of the region you are in.</p>", "price": 150, "rarity": "", "pocket": "item"}, "effects": [], "source": "Core 3.0", "flags": {}, "_stats": {"systemId": "pokerole", "systemVersion": "v3.0", "coreVersion": "3.348", "createdTime": 1670695293664, "modifiedTime": 1784006564.932456, "lastModifiedBy": "Generator"}}
{"_id": "b767bde32cb17a87", "name": "Remedy", "type": "item", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "<p>This powder leaves a horrid aftertaste. Pokémon will only eat it if they are injured, and even so, they'll resent you for days.</p>", "price": 450, "rarity": "", "pocket": "medicine"}, "effects": [], "source": "Core 3.0", "flags": {}, "_stats": {"systemId": "pokerole", "systemVersion": "v3.0", "coreVersion": "3.348", "createdTime": 1670695293664, "modifiedTime": 1784006564.940846, "lastModifiedBy": "Generator"}}
{"_id": "6e9f42e893a28a2f", "name": "Revival Herb", "type": "item", "img": "systems/pokerole/images/items/revival-herb.png", "system": {"description": "<p>It may be its magical properties or just its awful flavor, but this herb will get you back into consciousness numbing all the pain away. Very rare to find. Restore conciousness & Full HP.</p>", "price": 2800, "rarity": "", "pocket": "medicine"}, "effects": [], "source": "Core 3.0", "flags": {}, "_stats": {"systemId": "pokerole", "systemVersion": "v3.0", "coreVersion": "3.348", "createdTime": 1670695293664, "modifiedTime": 1784006564.949042, "lastModifiedBy": "Generator"}}
{"_id": "2f8958354b528416", "name": "Revive", "type": "item", "img": "systems/pokerole/images/items/revive.png", "system": {"description": "<p>A small energy shard that brings a fainted Human or Pokémon back into conciousness and stabilizes all their wounds. Restore conciousness & 1 HP.</p>", "price": 1500, "rarity": "", "pocket": "medicine"}, "effects": [], "source": "Core 3.0", "flags": {}, "_stats": {"systemId": "pokerole", "systemVersion": "v3.0", "coreVersion": "3.348", "createdTime": 1670695293664, "modifiedTime": 1784006564.957277, "lastModifiedBy": "Generator"}}
{"_id": "dcddcafc8d0b9555", "name": "Ring Target", "type": "item", "img": "systems/pokerole/images/items/ring-target.png", "system": {"description": "<p>There is no escaping harm when you have a target on your back. Remove all immunities of the user.</p>", "price": null, "rarity": "Not for Sale", "pocket": "heldItem"}, "effects": [], "source": "Core 3.0", "flags": {}, "_stats": {"systemId": "pokerole", "systemVersion": "v3.0", "coreVersion": "3.348", "createdTime": 1670695293664, "modifiedTime": 1784006564.965353, "lastModifiedBy": "Generator"}}
{"_id": "c0110c849830d207", "name": "Rockium Z", "type": "item", "img": "systems/pokerole/images/items/rockium-z.png", "system": {"description": "<p>It converts Z-Power into crystals that upgrade Rock-type moves to Rock-type Z-Moves.</p>", "price": null, "rarity": "Not for Sale", "pocket": "heldItem"}, "effects": [], "source": "Core 3.0+", "flags": {}, "_stats": {"systemId": "pokerole", "systemVersion": "v3.0", "coreVersion": "3.348", "createdTime": 1670695293664, "modifiedTime": 1784006564.973865, "lastModifiedBy": "Generator"}}
{"_id": "8f66c2f8a4409d9d", "name": "Rocky Helmet", "type": "item", "img": "systems/pokerole/images/items/rocky-helmet.png", "system": {"description": "<p>The best defense is a good offense Deal 1 damage to a foe hitting the user with a Non-Ranged Physical Move.</p>", "price": null, "rarity": "Not for Sale", "pocket": "heldItem"}, "effects": [], "source": "Core 3.0", "flags": {}, "_stats": {"systemId": "pokerole", "systemVersion": "v3.0", "coreVersion": "3.348", "createdTime": 1670695293664, "modifiedTime": 1784006564.982872, "lastModifiedBy": "Generator"}}
